Commentary Text: Maxwell to Moeen Ali, out Moeen Ali Run Out!! A sensational bit of fielding by the debutant. Moeen Ali rocks back and cuts this to backward point, and Prabhusessai stationed there stops it with a dive to his right. He was off for a single, but the fielder fires in a rocket throw at the keeper's end. Karthik completes the formalities and Chennai Super Kings are in trouble once again. Moeen had no chance to get back in, fantastic fielding that. Moeen Ali run out (Prabhudessai/Karthik) 3(8)

Commentary Text: Hazlewood to Gaikwad, out Lbw!! Gaikwad has been given out LBW and he has decided to challenge the decision. He reckons the impact was slightly high, and that might save him. Nothing on UltraEdge, there's no bat involved. Oh, that's just clipping the stumps and Hazlewood gets his first wicket of IPL 2022. A back of a length delivery by Hazlewood and the batter looks to swipe it across the line. Gets beaten as the ball jags back in and strikes him on the back pad. Pitching in line, impact in line and it's umpire's call on hitting. Gaikwad's poor run continues. Played a couple of good looking boundaries, but departs soon after. Gaikwad lbw b Hazlewood 17(16) [4s-3]
